      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774721308,
      "updated": 1774725577
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8191b0000000000a20ce8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e961818881b254c672b15c8af97024f6]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774721308,
      "updated": 1774730630
    },
    {
      "id": "69c83d86000000000043db21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774730631,
      "updated": 1774730631
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8191b0000000000a20ce9",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774721308,
      "updated": 1774721310
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82628000000000043db12",
      "text": "[** ページタイトルを考える]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774724648,
      "updated": 1774726610
    },
    {
      "id": "69c819280000000000a20cec",
      "text": " この[ページタイトル]、変えたほうがいいかも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774721320,
      "updated": 1774724687
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82ddf000000000043db1a",
      "text": "　　元のタイトル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774726624,
      "updated": 1774726627
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82de1000000000043db1b",
      "text": " 　　2026/03/29(suto3)",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774726625,
      "updated": 1774726629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8198c0000000000a20cf1",
      "text": "　　 　[記号的]すぎる",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1774721420,
      "updated": 1774741491
    },
    {
      "id": "69c86b4b0000000000ba5db7",
      "text": "　　 　人間からみたらノイズみたいなもん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774742348,
      "updated": 1774742439
    },
    {
      "id": "69c819480000000000a20cee",
      "text": "  では、どんなタイトルがいいのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774721352,
      "updated": 1774724687
    },
    {
      "id": "69c824b3000000000043db0d",
      "text": "  　[よいページタイトルとは]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1774724276,
      "updated": 1774741485
    },
    {
      "id": "69c825b7000000000043db0e",
      "text": "  人間が読むページでは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774724535,
      "updated": 1774745080
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875f30000000000460923",
      "text": " 　 人間が読む前提で、人間にとって読みやすいページタイトルにすればいい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774745075,
      "updated": 1774745082
    },
    {
      "id": "69c837b2000000000043db20",
      "text": "  では、人間が読まないページでは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774729138,
      "updated": 1774729166
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875b30000000000460922",
      "text": "   コンピュータが処理しやすいページタイトルにすればいい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774745011,
      "updated": 1774748502
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8837700000000000b67ec",
      "text": "   `prefix-userid-YYYY-MM-DD`みたいなやつ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774748535,
      "updated": 1774748602
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8907900000000004068bb",
      "text": "   例: [log-suto3-2026-03-29]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774751866,
      "updated": 1774751880
    },
    {
      "id": "69c826bf000000000043db13",
      "text": " ページタイトルを考えることは[認知負荷]が大きい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774724800,
      "updated": 1774724894
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8248b000000000043db0c",
      "text": "　　ページタイトルを考えなくていい井戸端日記の発明は偉大",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774724235,
      "updated": 1774724921
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82a37000000000043db17",
      "text": " ページタイトル変更",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774725688,
      "updated": 1774727304
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82a5a000000000043db19",
      "text": " 　ページタイトルをちょくちょく変えることになるかも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774725722,
      "updated": 1774727304
    },
    {
      "id": "69c83036000000000043db1e",
      "text": " 　ページタイトルはもっと雑に替えていい、よね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774727223,
      "updated": 1774727304
    },
    {
      "id": "69c82973000000000043db15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774725491,
      "updated": 1774725491
    },
    {
      "id": "69c834590000000000a4aefe",
      "text": "[** infobox日記のこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728282,
      "updated": 1774729404
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8346f0000000000a4aeff",
      "text": " [個人日記ページ]ととらえる向きがある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728303,
      "updated": 1774728407
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8347b0000000000a4af00",
      "text": "　むしろ、既存の日記ページの解体と再構成だと思う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728315,
      "updated": 1774728602
    },
    {
      "id": "69c835590000000000a4af03",
      "text": "　これまでの日記にはない可能性があるのではないか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728538,
      "updated": 1774728579
    },
    {
      "id": "69c834d90000000000a4af01",
      "text": " ひとつの考え方として…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728410,
      "updated": 1774741214
    },
    {
      "id": "69c866ea0000000000ba5db1",
      "text": " 　井戸端日記は集中型共同日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774741227,
      "updated": 1774741252
    },
    {
      "id": "69c867130000000000ba5db2",
      "text": " 　infobox日記は分散型共同日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774741268,
      "updated": 1774741291
    },
    {
      "id": "69c867320000000000ba5db3",
      "text": " 　といえるかも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774741298,
      "updated": 1774741307
    },
    {
      "id": "69c835550000000000a4af02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774728533,
      "updated": 1774728533
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9050a0000000000332bd1",
      "text": "[** 本日のX]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774781706,
      "updated": 1774781737
    },
    {
      "id": "69c904d70000000000332bcd",
      "text": ">[https://x.com/kureakurea01/status/2038051859756404880 @kureakurea01]: 日本に向けて、アメリカ勢のバーベキュー発信が始まった。しかもそれは、政治でもない。市場でもない。軍事でもない。ただ「見ろ、うちの肉を」という、あまりにも平和で、あまりにも豪快な文化の挨拶だった。この流れの何がいいかというと、誰も難しい説明をしていないことだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774781655,
      "updated": 1774781698
    },
    {
      "id": "69c905020000000000332bcf",
